kotlin
    multiplatform
        platform:
            jvm
            js
            android
            native
                ios
                linux
                windows
                mac
                embedded
                    stm32
        code-sharing
            memungkinkan mengelompokkan beberapa kode seusai fungsi masing-masing as module
            module:
                common module:      platform-agnostic code
                platform module:    platform-specific code
                regular module:     umum tapi target platform tertentu?
    multiparadigm
        oop
        fp

kotlin for server-side application
    why
        expressiveness
        scalability
        interoperability:   kotlin is fully compatible with all java framework
        migration
        tooling
    framework
        spring  (java)
        vert.x
        ktor
        kotlinx.html
        exposed (SQL framework)

kotlin for android application
    why
        compatibility (fully compatible with JDK 6)
        performance
        interoperability
        compilation time

kotlin as investment
    kelebihan di aspek produktivitas
        ringkas (concise)
        interoperable
        tool-friendly

kotlin characteristics
    modern and concise  -> no semicolon (??? is it even modern?)
    pragmatic
    safe
        memory safe     -> no NullPointerException (null safety)
            kotlin membedakan objek yang boleh null atau tidak boleh null
    statically typed
        has type inference btw
    free and open source

